Sentencas: The impedance response of a Pt/YSZ (yttria-stabilized zirconia) interface at 900 degrees C is modified by the passage of direct currents.
Titulo: Transient and permanent effects of direct current on oxygen transfer across YSZ-Electrode interfaces

Sentencas: The initial steady-state impedance spectra are different from those taken after current interruption.
Titulo: Transient and permanent effects of direct current on oxygen transfer across YSZ-Electrode interfaces

Sentencas: The latter evolve toward a new steady state.
Titulo: Transient and permanent effects of direct current on oxygen transfer across YSZ-Electrode interfaces

Sentencas: The magnitude and equilibration kinetics of this effect are complex functions of the direction and magnitude of the applied current and the history of gas exposure.
Titulo: Transient and permanent effects of direct current on oxygen transfer across YSZ-Electrode interfaces

Sentencas: An equivalent circuit that models the evolving changes in the impedance spectra is proposed.
Titulo: Transient and permanent effects of direct current on oxygen transfer across YSZ-Electrode interfaces

Sentencas: The analysis of the effect may provide an insight into the mechanism of the anodic and cathodic interfacial reactions in a solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: Transient and permanent effects of direct current on oxygen transfer across YSZ-Electrode interfaces
